title: Implemented ability to combine series
message:
Implemented ability to combine series

App prompts users to combine similar series (can be enabled / disabled) and merges up to two similar series into one. Fixes #37

title: Offset foul values to prevent rows from being written twice
message:
Offset foul values to prevent rows from being written twice

By using 0-7 for foul values, when the db was upgraded, a value of 1 was replaced by 3 then that 3 was later replaced by 1, causing the fouls to be incorrectly updated. This has been fixed.

title: Changed storage of fouls from strings to ints
message:
Changed storage of fouls from strings to ints

Fouls were being stored as strings of which balls had fouls, which took more memory than simply representing these values as a value from 0-7, as they are now. Fixes #19

title: Changed frame storage from strings to ints
message:
Changed frame storage from strings to ints

The resulting frames after each ball were being stored as strings, which led to a lot of duplicated data. Strings have been replaced with ints (actually bytes) which cuts down a lot of storage required for items. First commit towards #19
